io		<font face="SILDoulosIPA">[jo]	</font> a back mid vowel with palatal on-glide
iu		<font face="SILDoulosIPA">[ju]	</font> a back close vowel with palatal on-glide

ua		<font face="SILDoulosIPA">[wa]	</font> an open vowel with labial on-glide
ue		<font face="SILDoulosIPA">[wE]	</font> a front mid vowel with labial on-glide
ui		<font face="SILDoulosIPA">[wi]	</font> a front close vowel with labial on-glide
