<lx "GIhA selma'o"> XE "GIhA selma'o"
   
<lx "KE selma'o"> XE "KE selma'o"
   
<cx "tensed logical connectives: in gihek…ke"> XE "tensed logical connectives: in gihek…ke"
   Between a gihek and "ke”, as in:
