<p>
<p>
Specifies simple time directions (future, past, or neither).
<p>
<p>
<pre>mi pu klama le zarci
	I [past] go-to the market.
	I went to the market.
</pre>
<p>
<lx "RAhO: selma'o catalog"> XE "RAhO: selma'o catalog"
   
